<Base title="About AgentAI Guide — AI Tools Reviews for Realtors" description="AgentAI Guide is an independent publication helping real estate agents discover, evaluate, and use AI tools to close more deals and save time.">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto prose prose-green prose-lg">
    <h1>About AgentAI Guide</h1>
    <p>AgentAI Guide is an independent resource for real estate agents who want to work smarter with AI. We test, review, and explain AI tools — so you can skip the research and get straight to results.</p>

    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>Every week brings a new AI tool claiming to revolutionize real estate. We cut through the noise with honest, practical reviews based on real testing — not vendor talking points. Our goal: help agents find tools that actually work in daily practice.</p>

    <h2>Our Team</h2>

    <div class="not-prose border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-6 mb-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-1">Alex Morgan — Founder &amp; Lead Reviewer</h3>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-3">Real estate technology consultant · 8 years in residential real estate · Licensed in California</p>
      <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Alex spent eight years as a residential agent before moving into real estate technology consulting. He has evaluated over 60 AI and proptech products and advises independent brokerages on digital tools adoption. Alex writes the in-depth tool reviews and ChatGPT prompt guides on this site.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="not-prose border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-6 mb-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-1">Sarah Chen — Research &amp; Market Analysis</h3>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-3">Data analyst · Former MLS data team · Specializes in proptech research</p>
      <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Sarah brings a data-first perspective to our coverage. With a background on an MLS data team, she focuses on market analysis tools, AI valuation platforms, and CMA software. Sarah verifies all statistics and data sources cited in our articles.</p>
    </div>

    <h2>Editorial Standards</h2>
    <p>We test every tool we review. Our ratings reflect hands-on evaluation, not sponsored placement. When we include affiliate links, we disclose it — always. We update reviews when products change significantly.</p>

    <h2>Affiliate Disclosure</h2>
    <p>Some links on AgentAI Guide are affiliate links. If you click through and make a purchase, we may earn a commission at no extra cost to you. This helps us keep the site free. We only recommend tools we have personally evaluated and would recommend regardless of commission.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions, corrections, or partnership inquiries: <a href="mailto:hello@agentai-guide.com">hello@agentai-guide.com</a></p>
  </div>
</Base>
